blockquote>有腦？</blockquote><br />\n用左黎裝屎算唔算有"},{"pid":"def499aaf4e16324d3ee4a71a1411c6b6cac283b","tid":228000,"uid":53923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:32:37.000Z","msg":"食齋係宗教原因<br />\n宗教有得話戇唔戇鳩架咩？<br />\n用佛教做例子<br />\n唔食肉係為左唔殺生<br />\n素肉材料多數係豆腐豆卜<br />\n過程中冇殺動物唔會殺生<br />\n咁有咩問題？<br />\n當然我覺得虔誠既人齋口齋心唔會食素肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但普通素食者都會食素肉嘅<br />\n齋鋪唔係只係做食齋嘅人生意架嘛<br />\n素肉都係多一種食材選擇啫<br />\n<br />\n食唔食齋/素係個人選擇<br />\n冇人chur你一齊食咪得<br />\n唔洗專登出post話人戇鳩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fbea8c52d7ae20c8a20703eeeec058ae6d4e3a","tid":228000,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食齋係宗教原因<br />\n宗教有得話戇唔戇鳩架咩？<br />\n用佛教做例子<br />\n唔食肉係為左唔殺生<br />\n素肉材料多數係豆腐豆卜<br />\n過程中冇殺動物唔會殺生<br />\n咁有咩問題？<br />\n當然我覺得虔誠既人齋口齋心唔會食素肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但普通素食者都會食素肉嘅<br />\n齋鋪唔係只係做食齋嘅人生意架嘛<br />\n素肉都係多一種食材選擇啫<br />\n<br />\n食唔食齋/素係個人選擇<br />\n冇人chur你一齊食咪得<br />\n唔洗專登出post話人戇鳩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係為宗教而食齋，再站係道德高地就係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾宗教撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc21d242ffc53e210e4227e2019a81c0f1a30bb8","tid":228000,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:50:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有肉唔食 學動物食草</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dcfbaab3fdb9cf254fc4c3b3dc222b66d4fa40","tid":228000,"uid":37130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有肉唔食 學動物食草</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1ea9d3e80cb85ff4ebc05b405abff0e99572c5","tid":228000,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"人地整到肉咁係為咗非素食者容易接受，而唔係素食者屎忽痕想食肉。<br />\n樓主唔好用屎忽諗野啦"},{"pid":"26d4be601bc6cf6f42eb644ca81d2c962f1ec2b2","tid":228000,"uid":27256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"但係植物都有生命喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好殘忍啊"},{"pid":"6b7e7288ab8367900e9140dd5da32d459cb3466b","tid":228000,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係on9，有肉唔食。食齋肉仲on9，要特登整返啲似肉嘅野黎食，食緊果時個腦究竟諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食齋OK 但食齋鴨肉 雞肉 叉燒真心唔明<br />\n仲話好似食緊肉咁 口感似食<br />\n呢D齋肉仲高納高糖過真肉啦"},{"pid":"5bb809ca19d651c781b5fe9ea232625268e9ce83","tid":228000,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食齋係宗教原因<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">宗教有得話戇唔戇鳩架咩？</span><br />\n用佛教做例子<br />\n唔食肉係為左唔殺生<br />\n素肉材料多數係豆腐豆卜<br />\n過程中冇殺動物唔會殺生<br />\n咁有咩問題？<br />\n當然我覺得虔誠既人齋口齋心唔會食素肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但普通素食者都會食素肉嘅<br />\n齋鋪唔係只係做食齋嘅人生意架嘛<br />\n素肉都係多一種食材選擇啫<br />\n<br />\n食唔食齋/素係個人選擇<br />\n冇人chur你一齊食咪得<br />\n唔洗專登出post話人戇鳩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔使我答啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}